com.yy.transvod.player.log

类 TLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yy.transvod.player.log.TLog

  • public final class TLog
extends java.lang.Object
    Player engine Log center.

    if you wanna to listen to the player engine log, do as follows:
    step 1: implement the OnLogCallback interface.
    step 2: call registerLogger(Object) to regist.

        public static void setLevel(int level)
        Sets level.

        the level is same to system Log. Log VERBOSE = 2, DEBUG = 3, INFO = 4, WARN = 5,ERROR = 6.

        参数:
        level - the level
